    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"所有Frontend实例（frontend-0/1/2）均出现大量HTTP 500错误（总计435次）和context canceled错误，表明上游服务不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"数据库连接层\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService到TiDB的查询延迟显著增加，表明数据库层存在性能瓶颈或连接问题\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 关键发现分析：\n\n1. **根因定位**：ProductCatalogService是问题的核心，其GetProduct和ListProducts接口延迟激增5000-30000倍，导致调用链上游服务（Frontend）出现大量超时和错误。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - ProductCatalogService性能严重下降\n   - → Frontend服务调用超时（context canceled）\n   - → 用户端收到HTTP 500错误\n\n3. **异常特征**：\n   - 所有Frontend实例（0/1/2）都受到影响，说明问题具有系统性\n   - 异常集中在ProductCatalog相关操作，其他服务相对正常\n   - 存在\"transport is closing\"错误，表明连接层可能存在问题\n\n建议进一步检查ProductCatalogService的资源使用情况、数据库连接池状态以及TiDB数据库的性能指标。", "metric_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio (38.28 to 56.51), server_error_ratio (38.28 to 56.51), and rrt (12249.68 to 22968663.16) for frontend-1.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 38.28, server_error_ratio from 0.0 to 38.28, and rrt from 12249.68 to 22968663.16.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio (38.6) and client_error_ratio (38.6), along with increased rrt (7285.5 to 9558.46) and rrt_max (33601.0 to 32175.0).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio and client_error_ratio increased to 38.6, rrt increased by 0.2699, and rrt_max decreased slightly.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio (50.0) and client_error_ratio (50.0) for shippingservice-0.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio and client_error_rati